{"tid":2232386,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"潘曉穎案，棄如敝屣 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-10-06T10:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T10:44:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6e631347b5bc51f07a94c3efdf1834fb563b56","tid":2232386,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201006/CQOGIQEPZVFBBC5BLIOK5MOWLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201006%2FCQOGIQEPZVFBBC5BLIOK5MOWLE%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKCT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=7388aeab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201006%2FCQOGIQEPZVFBBC5BLIOK5MOWLE%2F&h=309d8310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201006/CQOGIQEPZVFBBC5BLIOK5MOWLE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n潘曉穎案，棄如敝屣 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pQHtH5n2XY5hNUxpKgnxZQqarmQ=/790x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PS7VZPFURVHBTM6MEATH6UNIRI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpQHtH5n2XY5hNUxpKgnxZQqarmQ%3D%2F790x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPS7VZPFURVHBTM6MEATH6UNIRI.png&h=25593566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民建聯FB圖片<br />\n<br />\n二零一八年二月，有陳同佳者，攜女友潘曉穎赴臺灣，殺人棄屍，隻身逃回香港。潘母向民建聯求助，結果是鄭月娥政府乘機修訂《逃犯條例》，把引渡疑犯範圍擴至臺灣以至全中國，激起香港連場民變；而修例不成之後，潘曉穎案就給棄如敝屣。潘母最近對《立場新聞》記者說：「我們當初彷徨無計，於是求助民建聯，想不到引起這麼多事，現在非常內疚。」<br />\n<br />\n民建聯是中共旗下政黨，能通天聽，小民不察者往往就視為法力無邊救苦救難觀世音，否則潘母為什麼向民建聯而非民主派求援手。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而中共最擅長把壞事變成好事，為其所用。一九四六年七月，中國民主同盟兩名親共文人李公樸、聞一多相繼遇刺身死，一般人自然認定是國民黨所為，反國民政府浪潮一時席捲全國學界，毛澤東就為之歡呼：「蔣介石進犯軍和人民解放軍的戰爭，是第一條戰線；正義學生和蔣介石政府的鬥爭，是第二條。」美國也因此斷絕援助蔣政府。所以，李、聞甚至潘曉穎，都可以說是死得好，潘母不明白而已。"}]}